test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [70] == [14, 14, 14, 14, 14, 14, ...]
  At index 0 diff: 70 != 14
  Right contains 8 more items, first extra item: 14
  Full diff:
  - [14, 14, 14, 14, 14, 14, 14, 14, 14]
  + [70]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [70] == [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, ...]

  Right contains 8 more items, first extra item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0]
  + [70]
